latestIgtvVideos.title: •ASSAM FLOODS•  FACE ART  Raising voice through my art
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
you will get the full video on YouTube..link is in my bio..

I'm trying to portray the current scenario of assam through my art.. people and animals are dying in assam and national media is least bothered about it.. so it's just a way of raising my voice so that people out side assam got to know about this condition of assam.
